name: Dogging Dublin
description:
Seminal zine set in Dublins fair city. Follows our protagonist, real life girlo and sexual goddess, Clitriona UÃ­ Bhriain on her misadventures, life discoveries and frigs.
Articles include The Marauders Frig, Muff Defence, Is Hentai Ruining The Porn Industry, and many more. Illustrated for your imaginary pleasure.

http://doggingdublin.tumblr.com/

name: How I Learned To Stop Worrying and Troll, Troll, TROLLLL zine
description: The internet has destroyed zines and facebook has ruined your life. People dedicate their whole days to trying to convince other people their opinion is wrong and invalid. I have since completely lost hope in much of humanity and now I pretend to be one of them, to "go native" and go on their forums and present a new type of antagonistic protest, which is ultimately pointless.

name: Gasmask Lady
description:
Do you cry when you are chopping onions? Fret not, this woman does also so she now wears a gasmask to protect her sobbing eyes.

High quality gilcee print on magnetic paper.
Measures 10" x 5"

name: Face Transplants

name: Death Metal Magnets
description:
Ever try to get your death metal band off the ground but couldn't find the right name?
This set is for you!

Featuring plenty of names to make combinations such as BESTIAL MAGDALENA SPLATTER, THE R.I.P. DIMEBAG'S, BIONIC EUCHARIST, WEEPING CHRONIC BONG and other glorious bands.

Magnets come in cool packaging which makes them an apt present.

Specs:
Type set in Illustrator
Gilcee Print on Magnetic Paper
Meticulous guillotine and handcut
Comes in pretty bag with labels on front and back, with design inside.
